			<div type="translation" xml:lang="de" org="uniform" sample="complete">
				<p>                                                <p>Für die Göttin <rs type="divine">Aventia</rs> und den <rs type="divine">Genius incolarum</rs>!</p>
                                                <p>Titus Ianuarius Florinus und Publius Domitius Didymus, (die) curatores coloniae, haben (dies) aus der jährlichen Spende (und) unter Beifügung von Sesterzen 1500 von ihrem eigenen (Geld aufgestellt).<br/>
                                </p>
                            </p>
			</div>
			<div type="translation" xml:lang="en" org="uniform" sample="complete">
				<p>                                                <p>To the goddess Aventia and the Genius incolarum!</p>
                                                <p>Titus Ianuarius Florinus and Publius Domitius Didymus, (the) curatores coloniae, have (errected this) from the annual offerings (and) by adding 1500 Sestertii from their own (money).<br/>
                                </p>
                            </p>
			</div>
